---
import "@/assets/styles/home/WhatsNewSection.css";
---
<section class="section">
  <h2 class="section-title">What's new.</h2>
  <div class="grid three">
    <div>
      <span class="emoji-above">⏳</span>
      <h3>Tithi & Time Tools</h3>
      <p>Explore traditional lunar calendar details alongside modern timestamps. Includes unit converters for daily use.</p>
      <a href="/vedic"><button class="button link">Learn more</button></a>
    </div>
    <div>
      <span class="emoji-above">🗺️</span>
      <h3>Culture Explorer</h3>
      <p>Travel through India's rich heritage with immersive maps and family tree explorations.</p>
      <a href="/clan"><button class="button link">Learn more</button></a>
    </div>
    <div>
      <span class="emoji-above">🧩</span>
      <h3>Display Modes</h3>
      <p>Visualize alphabets interactively: build vertical stacks, create flowing queues, or swipe through sliders in fun display formats.</p>
      <a href="/cards"><button class="button link">Learn more</button></a>
    </div>
  </div>
  <div class="grid three">
    <div>
      <span class="emoji-above">✏️</span>
      <h3>Draw & Learn</h3>
      <p> Tap letters to display matching images, then draw over them with customizable colors and backgrounds.</p>
      <a href="/draw"><button class="button link">Learn more</button></a>
    </div>
    <div>
      <span class="emoji-above">📖</span>
      <h3>Knowledge Glossary</h3>
      <p>Learn about months, days, sun signs, country flags, seasons, colors, shapes, and times of the day in an accessible format.</p>
      <a href="/glossary"><button class="button link">Learn more</button></a>
    </div>
    <div>
      <span class="emoji-above">🖌️</span>
      <h3>Creative Studio</h3>
      <p>"Design beautiful quotes or custom text visuals with the Text and Quote Designer tools— perfect for creative expression.</p>
      <a href="/canvas"><button class="button link">Learn more</button></a>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>